                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-170-off941 t18280529-170-cd942"></join>, 1 tea-pot, value 5s.; 1 tea-caddy, value 3s.; 7 chimney ornaments, value 7s.; 1 basin, value 3s.; 2 spoons, value 1s.; 1 rummer-glass, value 2s., and 1 pair of boots, value 3s.
